              .card-text.mt-3
                h6
                  strong Instructions

                p
                  | Create/Repair the necessary views to facilitate CRUD of a metahuman:
                ul.ml-2
                  li
                    | index
                  li
                    | show
                  li
                    | new
                  li
                    | edit
                  li
                    | form (partial)
